      • GPBF_UNSUPPORTED_MASK

        private static final int GPBF_UNSUPPORTED_MASK
        Supported General Purpose Bit Flags Mask. Bit mask of bits not supported. Note: The only bit that we will enforce at this time is the encrypted bit. Although other bits are not supported, we must not enforce them as this could break some legitimate use cases (See http://b/8617715).
